    <entry>
      <title>一段代码能运行的蜕变之旅</title>
      <link href="/project/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/"/>
      <url>/project/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="蜕变须知"><a href="#蜕变须知" class="headerlink" title="蜕变须知"></a>蜕变须知</h1><p>一个可执行文件的前世今生是历经波折的，它需要经历以下过程:</p><p><img src="/project/project/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B.jpg"></p><p>博主将在虚拟机上完成这一过程，重点放在汇编和链接部分。</p><h1 id="本次过程的目录结构"><a href="#本次过程的目录结构" class="headerlink" title="本次过程的目录结构"></a>本次过程的目录结构</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><figcaption><span>README.md</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">├── include</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">│ └── test.h</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">├── lib</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">│ ├── libtest.a</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">│   main</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">└── src</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"> ├── main.cpp</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"> └── test.c</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>说明：静态库libtest.a,main.cpp的头文件放在test.cpp中</p><h1 id="旅程启动！"><a href="#旅程启动！" class="headerlink" title="旅程启动！"></a>旅程启动！</h1><ul><li><p><strong>创建目录结构和文件：</strong></p><p><img src="/project/project/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA.jpg"></p><p><img src="/project/project/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%95%E7%A4%BA.jpg"></p></li><li><p><strong>编写代码</strong></p><p>可以打开文件夹点击文件直接code,也可以运用vim</p><p><img src="/project/project/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E7%BC%96%E5%86%99.jpg"></p><p>vim:</p><p><img src="/project/project/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/vim.jpg"></p><p>博主运行的代码很简单：</p><p>test.h</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">ifndef</span> TEST_H</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> TEST_H</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">printHello</span><span class="params">()</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">endif</span> </span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>test.cpp</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&quot;test.h&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">printHello</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    std::cout &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;Hello from libtest!&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; std::endl;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>main.cpp</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&quot;test.h&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printHello</span>();</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>编译源文件并创建目标文件：</strong></p><p>在运行下列命令是出现如下错误</p><p><img src="/project/project/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/mistake1.jpg"></p><p>原因是头文件并不在当前的目录里，我们需要去寻找头文件,<strong>在这里我们采用-I的形式</strong></p><p><img src="/project/project/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/touwj.jpg"></p><p><img src="/project/project/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/mistak2.jpg"></p><p>但是又出现了错误，这是怎么回事呢？原来是我们需要把目标文件放在一个路径里，而我们此时没有创建。所以创建一个obj文件存放目标文件</p><p>再次执行,就生成了main和test的目标文件</p><p><img src="/project/project/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/obj.jpg"></p></li><li><p><strong>创建静态库 <code>libtest.a</code>：</strong></p><p>注意我们创建静态库的时候会出现权限不够的错误，因此命令为</p><p><img src="/project/project/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/staticlib.jpg"></p></li><li><p><strong>编译主程序：</strong></p><p>接下来就可以编译主程序啦！但是还是有错误，原来我们需要将main文件放置在一个路径里</p><p><img src="/project/project/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/mistake3.jpg"></p><p>创建好一个bin文件夹，就能正确编译了</p><p><img src="/project/project/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/all.jpg"></p></li><li><p><strong>运行主程序</strong></p><p><img src="/project/project/2024/02/01/%E4%B8%80%E6%AE%B5%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%9C%95%E5%8F%98%E4%B9%8B%E6%97%85/%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C.jpg"></p><p>（爱来自libtest!!!)</p></li></ul><h1 id="命令整理"><a href="#命令整理" class="headerlink" title="命令整理"></a>命令整理</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">mkdir</span> -p project/include project/lib project/src</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">touch</span> project/README.md</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">touch</span> project/include/test.h</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">touch</span> project/src/main.cpp</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">touch</span> project/src/test.cpp</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#在project/src 路径下</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#创建obj文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line">g++ -c main.cpp -I../include -o ../obj/main.o</span><br><span class="line">g++ -c test.cpp -I../include -o ../obj/main.o</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#创建静态库</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo ar rcs lib/libtest.a obj/test.o</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#编译主程序</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#创建bin文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line">g++ obj/main.o -Iinclude -Llib -ltest -o bin/main</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#运行主程序</span></span><br><span class="line">project/bin/main</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>Bhuman 2023 环境部署</title>
      <link href="/project/2024/01/30/Bhuman-2023-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/"/>
      <url>/project/2024/01/30/Bhuman-2023-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="BHuman-2023-Windows环境部署"><a href="#BHuman-2023-Windows环境部署" class="headerlink" title="BHuman 2023 Windows环境部署"></a>BHuman 2023 Windows环境部署</h1><p>博主依据BHuamn的官方文档逐步配置环境,期间出现了较多问题和需要注意的事项，特此整理出这篇博客，希望能帮助到大家！<a href="https://github.com/bhuman/BHumanCodeRelease">点击此处跳转BHuamnCoderealse</a>以及<a href="https://docs.b-human.de/coderelease2023/getting-started/initial-setup/">BHuman setup</a>。</p><h2 id="代码下载"><a href="#代码下载" class="headerlink" title="代码下载"></a>代码下载</h2><p>可进入github直接clone或者下载压缩包，但官方代码还需要要额外配置。<br>博主这里有直接的代码压缩包和必要的库<a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1DDZfELteZrhSOPlQ8hrsTQ">https://pan.baidu.com/s/1DDZfELteZrhSOPlQ8hrsTQ</a><br>  提取码：26aw  </p><p><strong>注意要将all文件夹放在util文件目录下！</strong>   </p><h2 id="软件准备"><a href="#软件准备" class="headerlink" title="软件准备"></a>软件准备</h2><ul><li>VS 2022<br>若初次安装可在安装时勾选使用c++的桌面开发、通用Windows平台开发即可，视情况还可安装其他以后需要的功能比如python开发等<br><img src="/project/images/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240131154616.jpg"></li><li>CMake 3.21.2<br>注意版本与官方文档要求的一致</li></ul><h2 id="编译代码"><a href="#编译代码" class="headerlink" title="编译代码"></a>编译代码</h2><ul><li>双击位于目录下的generate.cmd，使其能正常运行并自动pop出（出现error则对应error去检查）<strong>此时会生成Build文件夹</strong></li></ul><p><code>Make/Windows/generate.cmd</code><br><img src="/project/images/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240131161637.jpg"><br><em>例如博主一开始CMake版本不匹配并且VS不是2022版本出现了如下错误</em><br><img src="/project/images/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91_20240131160615.jpg">  </p><ul><li>在<code>Build/Windows/CMake</code>找到<code>B-Human.sln</code>右键选择以VS 2022方式运行<br><img src="/project/images/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240131161637.jpg">  </li><li>设置为release方式，右键SimRobot，选择生成<br><img src="/project/images/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240131163107.jpg"><br><img src="/project/images/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240131163209.jpg">  </li><li>博主在release遇到了如下错误<br><img src="/project/images/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240131163600.jpg"><br>通过调整项目属性部分解决了<br><img src="/project/images/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240131162317.jpg"><br>但是还是出现常量中有换行符的问题，在CSDN搜索了一下解决方法，然后尝试在出现错误的地方（即有双引号的地方）在后引号前加了一个空格键，问题解决<br><img src="/project/images/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240131164101.jpg"><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/annjeff/article/details/90070344?ops_request_misc=%257B%2522request%255Fid%2522%253A%2522170653508116800185871336%2522%252C%2522scm%2522%253A%252220140713.130102334..%2522%257D&request_id=170653508116800185871336&biz_id=0&utm_medium=distribute.pc_search_result.none-task-blog-2~all~sobaiduend~default-1-90070344-null-null.142%5Ev99%5Epc_search_result_base7&utm_term=C2001&spm=1018.2226.3001.4187">链接</a>  </li><li>运行Simbot<br>项目正常运行后会弹出SimRobot程序，如图<br><img src="/project/images/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240131164409.jpg"><br>或者在<code>Build\Windows\SimRobot\Release</code>点击程序运行<br><img src="/project/images/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20240131164526.jpg"><br>从<code>Install/Scenes</code>选择文件打开，如果能成功打开则部署成功！</li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>Hello World</title>
      <link href="/project/2024/01/27/hello-world/"/>
      <url>/project/2024/01/27/hello-world/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Welcome to <a href="https://hexo.io/">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href="https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues">GitHub</a>.</p><h2 id="Quick-Start"><a href="#Quick-Start" class="headerlink" title="Quick Start"></a>Quick Start</h2><h3 id="Create-a-new-post"><a href="#Create-a-new-post" class="headerlink" title="Create a new post"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new <span class="string">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html">Writing</a></p><h3 id="Run-server"><a href="#Run-server" class="headerlink" title="Run server"></a>Run server</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/server.html">Server</a></p><h3 id="Generate-static-files"><a href="#Generate-static-files" class="headerlink" title="Generate static files"></a>Generate static files</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html">Generating</a></p><h3 id="Deploy-to-remote-sites"><a href="#Deploy-to-remote-sites" class="headerlink" title="Deploy to remote sites"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html">Deployment</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
  
  
